discovery-job-result
********************


Description
===========

A discovery job result representing a sensitive column. It can be one
of the following three types: NEW: A new sensitive column in the
target database that is not in the sensitive data model. DELETED: A
column that is present in the sensitive data model but has been
deleted from the target database. MODIFIED: A column that is present
in the target database as well as the sensitive data model but some of
its attributes have been modified.


Available Commands
==================

* delete

* get
